OL,7,FA bereaved woman says she believes the
OL,8,Fashes she received after her dad's
OL,9,Ffuneral may not be his - after using
OL,10,Fthe same family business now at the
OL,11,Fcentre of a police investigation.
OL,13,FIt comes after .
OL,15,FAimee's dad, Billy, passed away in
OL,16,FAugust 2020, but says she is now
OL,17,F"praying that her dad is not a part of
OL,18,Fthis", after an investigation into
OL,19,FLegacy funeral directors in Yorkshire.
