OL,3,C'I'm praying my dad is not part of
OL,4,Cthis': Bereaved woman questions dad's
OL,5,Cashes
OL,7,FShe said: "My dad was just the most
OL,8,Famazing man in the world, he was
OL,9,Feverybody's favourite.
OL,11,F"Certain family members have had the
OL,12,Fashes put into tattoos, and we don't
OL,13,Feven know if they are his ashes that
OL,14,Fhave been put into the tattoos.
OL,16,F"So we'll all be demanding that these
OL,17,Fashes are tested".
OL,19,FAimee said her family are now once
OL,20,Fagain going through "a really bad
OL,21,Ftime".
