OL,3,C'I'm praying my dad is not part of
OL,4,Cthis': Bereaved woman questions dad's
OL,5,Cashes
OL,7,F"We'll always miss my dad, we'll
OL,8,Falways grieve for my dad, it's a big
OL,9,Fgap in our lives - but when you think
OL,10,Fthat the dust is settling and then all
OL,11,Fthis is back - there's just so many
OL,12,Funcertainties."
OL,14,FAimee says she has spoken with the
OL,15,Fpolice to offer details of her dad's
OL,16,Ftattoos, any scars he may have had,
OL,17,Fand any further details.
OL,19,FBut, she said, the force told her it
OL,20,Fwould get back to her within 14 days.
