OL,3,C'I'm praying my dad is not part of
OL,4,Cthis': Bereaved woman questions dad's
OL,5,Cashes
OL,7,FShe said: "It's horrible, I just want
OL,8,Fto know now, 14 days is a long time to
OL,9,Fbe sat here wondering and guessing
OL,10,Fwith all kinds going through your head
OL,11,F- it's a really long time."
OL,13,FHumberside Police arrested two people
OL,14,Fon suspicion of prevention of a lawful
OL,15,Fand decent burial, fraud by false
OL,16,Frepresentation and fraud by abuse of
OL,17,Fposition.
OL,19,FThe pair have since been released on
OL,20,Fbail, and the investigation continues.
